# 📌 Part 2: General Prompt Template

Here’s a **prompt template** for anyone to create the same kind of portfolio with their own info.  
I’ve replaced your personal details with generic placeholders.

```text
You are ChatGPT or Gemini with full support for web development, TailwindCSS, SVG, AOS.js, and modern animated design.

Please build a modern, recruiter-friendly, premium portfolio website for a professional based on the following info:

---

## 👤 BASIC INFO
- Name: [YOUR NAME]  
- Location: [YOUR LOCATION]  
- Email: [YOUR EMAIL]  
- Phone: [YOUR PHONE]  
- LinkedIn: [YOUR LINKEDIN URL]  

---

## 🎓 EDUCATION
- [Your Degree & Field] – [College/University] ([Year Range])  
- [Your Diploma/Certification] – [Institution] ([Year Range])  

---

## 🏢 EXPERIENCE
- **[Job Title]** – [Company] ([Start Date] – [End Date]), [Location]  
- **[Job Title]** – [Company] ([Start Date] – [End Date]), [Location]  
- (Add as many as needed)

---

## 🛠️ PROJECTS (Expandable Sections)
1. **[Project Title]**  
   - [Detailed description of the project, technologies used, and outcomes]

(Add more projects if needed)

---

## 💼 SKILLS (Grouped with Icons)
### Technical Skills
- [Skill 1], [Skill 2], [Skill 3]  

### Soft Skills
- [Skill 1], [Skill 2], [Skill 3]  

### Software & Docs
- [Skill 1], [Skill 2], [Skill 3]  

---

## 📜 CERTIFICATIONS
1. [Certification Name] – [Platform/Institution]  
   [Certificate Link if available]  
2. [Certification Name] – [Platform/Institution]  
   (Add as many as needed)

---

## 🧩 UI / FEATURES TO INCLUDE
- TailwindCSS v3 dark-theme  
- Subtle rotating **gear-like background** (pure CSS SVG)  
- AOS.js scroll animations  
- Fully responsive layout  
- Mobile menu with hamburger icon  
- Modern font (`Inter`) and hover transitions  
- Resume download button  
- Profile image: `dp_profile.jpg`  
- Certification thumbnails with download links (`cert_name.jpg` + `.pdf`)  
- Smooth scroll & easy UX  
- Easy to deploy with GitHub Pages  

---

✅ OUTPUT REQUIREMENT:
Provide a **complete `index.html` code** that can be pasted and deployed immediately.  
Profile photo should be referenced as `dp_profile.jpg`.  
Certifications must follow the format: `cert_name.jpg` + `cert_name.pdf`.  
Ensure smooth animations, no lag, and professional readability.  
